{"tid":1579082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何君堯：對馬會取消賽事感到驚訝","createTime":"2019-09-18T11:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T12:31:57.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d143a2da03aa794c704a07201148dd7991c49026","tid":1579082,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:55:58.000Z","msg":"何君堯發聲明回應，今早（18日）天祿的其中一名合夥馬主何偉誠收到馬會賽事部鄭其龍來電，表示馬會管理階層對今晚在快活谷舉行的賽事感到擔心和顧慮，但馬會沒有要求天祿退出比賽，亦沒有暗示倘若繼續比賽，今晚賽事將會取消。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯表示對今晚取消賽事感到驚訝，憂慮取消比賽對香港作為國際大都會及香港在賽馬界之領導地位帶來負面影響。"},{"pid":"2f515108b694e298a1ccf23621df4e794ccbadec","tid":1579082,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190918/s00001/1568784717584/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190918%2Fs00001%2F1568784717584%2F&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=14e6da88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190918%2Fs00001%2F1568784717584%2F&h=4a729c3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190918/s00001/1568784717584/</a>"},{"pid":"786214e5335f599222405be59cd6398fbe7c5b54","tid":1579082,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:56:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://